posts.caption: Enjoying the golden hour this evening!
This dang duck bit my son!
Yay we got ice cream, I think I'm going to leave my wife soon.
Just bought this new house! Who wants to come annoy my new neighbors?
Took this pic of the ocean and some rocks, maybe I'll find treasures!
Leave a like on this post to be as happy as my puppy.
You know what they say, gamblers who quit were always one move away from winning big!
Help my dog got into my edibles and won't stop looking at me like this.
Chicken-mobile is finally in business. Hide your wives!
Went to the local farmers market today, found some great fruits to throw at my kids!
